---

<div class="culture wrapper">
  <div class="culture-text">
    <h2>Our<br /> Kelp<br /> Culture</h2>

    <p>We‚Äôre a small, senior team that takes the work seriously&thinsp;‚Äî&thinsp;and ourselves just seriously enough.</p>

