      So we don‚Äôt typically work more than 40 hours a week&thinsp;‚Äî&thinsp;and we don‚Äôt pretend that ‚Äúhustle‚Äù is a
      virtue. Instead, we make every hour count. Focused work. Fewer meetings. Clear priorities. No performative
