  </div>

  <div class="culture-media" data-lg-reveal="layer-to-right">
    <Picture
      src={cultureOfficeHonest}
      alt="Team reviewing work together"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
      widths={[480, 720, 960]}
      sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 50vw"
      inferSize
    />
  </div>

  <div class="culture-text">
    <h3>Specialists Who Actually Help Each Other</h3>

    <p>Each person on our team has deep expertise in a specific niche. At the same time, no one works in a silo.</p>

    <p>
      We help where help is needed. We review each other‚Äôs work. We care about the final outcome more than ownership or
      ego. That balance lets us move quickly without sacrificing quality.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="culture-media" data-lg-reveal="layer-to-left">
    <Picture
      src={cultureCollaboration}
      alt="Team collaborating around a desk"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
      widths={[480, 720, 960, 1200]}
      sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 50vw"
      inferSize
    />
  </div>

  <div class="culture-text">
    <h3>Tools Are Tools (Not a Religion)</h3>

    <p>We don‚Äôt chase trends&thinsp;‚Äî&thinsp;but we‚Äôre not allergic to change either.</p>

    <p>
